{"tid":611951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位鍾愛及支持李佳芯既巴絲打請入黎！！","createTime":"2018-03-31T13:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T14:27:35.000Z","uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8929eea2c866bfb18f26e84b99030e17e2a35387","tid":611951,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"各位鍾愛及支持李佳芯既巴絲打請入黎！！<br />\n<br />\n要幫助李佳芯贏朱千雪取得今屆超級女神聯賽既比賽，請立即click入以下網址，並投選<br />\n<br />\n荀云慧（請投正評）v朱千雪<br />\n<br />\n及<br />\n<br />\n李佳芯（請投正評）v馮盈盈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611133/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611133/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n剩返唔係一個鐘時間，投票就結束，而家荀云慧同朱千雪票數相差60票左右，仲有追平機會，請各位切勿 吝嗇你手上既一票！！！<br />\n<br />\n我作為李佳芯既粉絲先多謝各位巴絲既幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c944767701d11334850fcd21adf73906cd90670e","tid":611951,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/214541_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F214541_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2a5a2f4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee3e0b0a245646de5db64dad3058ff6edf1646cd","tid":611951,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a91c08cba392aaad0acbd50d70a507b4633f855","tid":611951,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee3e0b0a245646de5db64dad3058ff6edf1646cd","tid":611951,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"求下巴打幫幫忙荀云慧對朱千雪個欄投正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acc0acb4d7ad808b0048c1b897d5ad3f25d243e","tid":611951,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s